---
name: Dark Mode Technical
description: Style preset — Dark Mode Technical
tags: [style, technical, aspect-auto]
---
Render as a technical diagram with a dark charcoal or near-black background. Use light-colored text (white or light grey) and neon or high-contrast accent colors like cyan, green, and orange for lines, arrows, and highlights. Use a monospace or technical font for labels. Add subtle grid lines or dot patterns in the background. The result should look like a technical blueprint or engineering schematic -- precise, detailed, and developer-friendly.
